an.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78a5767c67a734e1d223ea6f73671068c2c34d99","tid":2515101,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T04:22:23.000Z","msg":"關於MC速度， 好多都係case by case咁嚟， 唔會條條啱用， 所以我都唔識教<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例子<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNwMbhW43yXwKxFUEKXczcuxe5cpUhQZsQrcoM1NXhopm?filename=rPLG2nM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrPLG2nM.png&h=aa8dd54d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n要嗰條線穿圓心(9, 10)同(s, t)， 斜率 -1/4<br />\n見斜率會判斷到係C或D， 跟著代(9, 10)<br />\n唔使真係計個常數項出嚟咁嘥時間， 你諗左手邊唔可以係全部正數就完， 呢個亦係C同D嘅主要分別。<br />\n<br />\n但正常學生落場會咁樣思考咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"050a784693ec7ece3a71bae50ca162084b01a2fc","tid":2515101,"uid":126679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"167eb6add139be56f6acd64a8658d43c55842c2b","tid":2515101,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44884f5ebe21ab174196d5e9e411d7d451e4135d","tid":2515101,"uid":109729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T04:03:37.000Z","msg":"想問會考巴有咩方法突破樽頸位？<br />\n無論係core定m2 都做熟過往dse pp<br />\n但上年同今年都係5**入面既低位（未知今年m2點）<br />\n<br />\n利伸：數學major，都係以爆機為目標，但未做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一直進步唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T04:15:55.000Z","msg":"爆機最緊要嘅係速度<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要高機率地爆機， 第一次完卷嘅時間就要控制喺一半以內。<br />\n<br />\n了解返自己平時衰咩， 記得遇過題目嘅伏位， 避免自己再踩中。 做完卷check卷嗰下， 要用出題角度去思考人哋會點樣伏班學生， 例如hemisphere vs sphere之類。<br />\n<br />\n至於M2就真係無研究到一套好方法， 我自己個分都唔係高<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加上近年都唔夠一半時間淨， 所以有時都會check漏眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n速度呢樣嘢就好睇自己做數嘅方法， 越多越快<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T04:50:54.000Z","msg":"其實M2 更加係喎<br />\n要考